Revision history for Perl extension Config::Wild.

1.5  Fri Aug 30 16:00:49 EDT 2013

[ENHANCEMENTS]

   * new method, getbool, converts value to boolean


1.4  Tue Aug 23 12:03:22 EDT 2011

[ENHANCEMENTS]

  * attributes may be specified via the constructor

  * new attribute, 'dir' allows chdir'ing to specified directory
    before loading config files

[OTHERS]

  * switch to Module::Install
  * switch to GPL3


1.3  Thu Sep 21 09:19:36 EDT 2006

  * first release into the Wild
